{
  "stem": "16473.2",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 10.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And not that, not that anybody could do anything in, in that basement area because there was no intimacy, because the women were here and the men were there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "But at least there could be some comment.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And I remember him kissing her, her kissing him.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So that's how my dad got, got out.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he was known as professor someone or another.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I forget what he was called.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And he lived there with the men.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Because the men and the women were segregated like they were, when the Nazis retreated, and as I said, the Russians came in, the Russians that came in were very young, very-- these Mongolian young guys, maybe about 17 or so.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "They were very childlike.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "They-- we knew, the rumor was, I don't know where we got the rumor, but we knew if they came in, they would steal and they would rape.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And so we didn't know it the first time, but we knew it after that.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "When these guys came in, they came, of course, to the women's quarters.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "The men were over there, they couldn't protect the women.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They came in the women's quarters and, and one of the guys eyes fell on this teenage girl that my mother was supposed to protect.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And first, because she had a bracelet, he took the bracelet.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And then he wanted to rape her.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And my mother, in her usual style, spoke up and said, you know, she's just a young girl, leave her alone.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And with that, she called attention to herself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And my mother and I were in the same bed and the guy was going to rape her.",
      "word_count": 18
    }
  ],
